{"tid":246006,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"港男谷肌要靚唔要命！亂啪藥搞到換腎","createTime":"2017-05-16T16:13:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T16:28:09.000Z","uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7dbbae6934de7068dcd163b66eceadc4d0944be9","tid":246006,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:13:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170516&amp;guid=56701150&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170516%26guid%3D56701150%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2FxqEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=f1f00ea5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170516%26guid%3D56701150%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=23a2fbb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170516&amp;guid=56701150&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n【新增短片】<br />\n健美人士練肌肉要小心，切勿亂用藥物達到大隻效果。醫管局中毒治療中心過去6年，收到5至6宗個案，全為健美人士濫用雄性激素類固醇、生長激素、胰島素等藥物，達至加強肌肉達至競技水平，最後出現不同器官衰竭情況，曾有個案同時使用13隻藥物後肺水腫，有個案則需要腎臟移植。<br />\n<br />\n威爾斯親王醫院中毒治療中心醫生王紹明表示，美國早有研究，高達80%健美人士有注射合成代謝雄激素類固醇，達致增大肌肉目的，近20%同時使用6至7種藥物。香港亦有個案出現，過去6年接獲5至6宗個案，主要為年輕健美人士，參加競賽為主。<br />\n<br />\n其中，一個34歲健美男子因急性肺水腫入院，並有血糖偏低情況，需要入深切治療部治療，並插喉協助呼吸。康復後醫生追查發現，他在外地購入合成代謝雄激素類固醇以及胰島素、生長激素共8隻注射用藥物，連同其他如瘦肉精等藥物，數月內同時間注射及服用13隻藥，目的刺激肌肉生長以參加健美比賽，結果影響心肌以致肺水腫出事。<br />\n<br />\n另一宗個案則涉及38歲男子，同樣為健美人士要谷肌肉，服用去氫表雄酮、可可中鹼等，結果出現蛋白尿、高血壓，並有「局灶性節段性」腎小球硬化症，最後要接受腎移植。<br />\n<br />\n王紹明強調，要達以肌肉肥大，應以鍛煉、營養補充及休息為方法，不要使用不明來歷藥物，如外國流行的雄激素類固醇，會出現心、肝、腎、生殖、精神及皮膚等不同副作用，其他如胰島素、生長激素等，則可導低血糖、假性腦瘤等副作用。"},{"pid":"4c1134d5193c35fe68b7dd2b1cb6ec3d50e58222","tid":246006,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:14:06.000Z","msg":"咁都有得換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依d一定排隊尾啦 自己搞成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e153b57271b6534c1f9e8a6b2866a15250c0d1b","tid":246006,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:15:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁都有得換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依d一定排隊尾啦 自己搞成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會理原因先排先得架"},{"pid":"c4c0288f6f6a542f82a9dba5b1f1f68ef728e982","tid":246006,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:16:36.000Z","msg":"搏盡無悔"},{"pid":"7c2627a3f739a30ab4f33ab8fca421958ebbaa6d","tid":246006,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:18:27.000Z","msg":"見到生晒瘡既師兄就知佢啪緊藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdddc2c1cdf913a2648840249c635e81a1fef999","tid":246006,"uid":57186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:19:07.000Z","msg":"抵死丫，一定平時無聽胡師傅講，亂食藥<br />\n完全做唔到健身健心健生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c088ddf0135de40d2e16427005d6c51619445c5b","tid":246006,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:22:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抵死丫，一定平時無聽胡師傅講，亂食藥<br />\n完全做唔到健身健心健生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你肯定胡師苦冇啪藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65fdca39264f72965b7f943b2543c13b3e85156b","tid":246006,"uid":70386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:28:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>抵死丫，一定平時無聽胡師傅講，亂食藥<br />\n完全做唔到健身健心健生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你肯定胡師苦冇啪藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockqu